      .our-vision__paragraph
        .paragraph__top
          p The way we live, work, play, and communicate is changing every single day with the rapid advance of technology, 
            | and this is why we want to be more than just a tech gadget company. 
            | We want to build a brand and a community that supports the constantly evolving lifestyles of the digital generation, and makes them feel understood and accepted.
          p We believe that all companies should be more than just a company; they should have a soul, too. 
            | This means that they not only focus on doing right by their consumers and developing great products, 
            | but that they hold their values close, stand up for what they believe in, and give back to the community.
        .paragraph__bottom
          p We strive to be a company with soul every single day; we aim to help people live lives that are as vibrant and fun as they are functional, 
            | and we dream of building a world where technology and sustainability go hand in hand.

